  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can forge an empowering bond among people who are at peace with one another. As a Magic action, you choose a number of willing creatures within 30 feet of you (this can include yourself) equal to your Proficiency Bonus. You create a magical bond among them for 10 minutes or until you use this feature again. While any bonded creature is within 30 feet of another, the creature can roll a d4 and add the number rolled to any D20 Test it makes. Each creature can add the d4 no more than once per turn.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest.</p>",
